grogginess</div>\n            <div class=\"ariya-product__benefit ariya-reveal ariya-delay-3\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14\"/><path d=\"M22 4L12 14.01l-3-3\"/></svg> Supports the body's own melatonin pathways</div>\n            <div class=\"ariya-product__benefit ariya-reveal ariya-delay-4\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14\"/><path d=\"M22 4L12 14.01l-3-3\"/></svg> Reduces nighttime stress and tension</div>\n            <div class=\"ariya-product__benefit ariya-reveal ariya-delay-5\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14\"/><path d=\"M22 4L12 14.01l-3-3\"/></svg> No artificial colors or preservatives</div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"ariya-product__price\">{{ product.price | money | default: '$44.99' }}</div>\n          <p class=\"ariya-product__price-sub\">60 capsules &bull; 30 servings</p>\n\n          <div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;flex-direction:column;\">\n            <form method=\"post\" action=\"/cart/add\" style=\"display:inline;\">\n              <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"id\" value=\"{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}\">\n              <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"quantity\" value=\"1\">\n              <button class=\"ariya-btn ariya-btn--primary\" type=\"submit\">Add to Cart</button>\n            </form>\n            <a href=\"{{ product.url | default: '/products/calm-nights' }}\" class=\"ariya-btn ariya-btn--secondary\" style=\"align-self:flex-start;font-size:0.8em;padding:8px 20px;\">View Full Details</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>",
