/></svg></div>\n        <h4>NSF GMP-Certified Facility</h4>\n        <p>Manufactured in an NSF GMP-certified, FDA-registered facility.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ariya-quality__card ariya-reveal ariya-delay-1\">\n        <div class=\"ariya-quality__card-icon\"><svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\n          <path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"/>\n          <path d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4\"/>\n        </svg></div>\n        <h4>Heavy Metal Tested</h4>\n        <p>Screened for heavy metals, microbial contamination, and pesticide residues.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ariya-quality__card ariya-reveal ariya-delay-2\">\n        <div class=\"ariya-quality__card-icon\"><svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"3\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" rx=\"2\"/><path d=\"M3 9h18M9 21V9\"/></svg></div>\n        <h4>Made in New York</h4>\n        <p>Manufactured in New York. Made in the USA with full traceability from source to shelf.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ariya-quality__card ariya-reveal ariya-delay-3\">\n        <div class=\"ariya-quality__card-icon\"><svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\n          <path d=\"M20 3c0 0-10 1-13 10-1.5 4.5 0 8 0 8\"/>\n          <path d=\"M20 3c0 0-1 10-11 14\"/>\n          <path d=\"M4 21l5-5\"/>\n        </svg></div>\n        <h4>Standardized Extracts</h4>\n        <p>Verified active compounds in every serving.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
